                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1050" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0143</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9171 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">嘉凯城集团股份有限公司借壳上市案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Case of China Calxon Group Company Limited Backdoor Listing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">戴娟萍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">嘉凯城集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">嘉凯城；借壳上市；价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">China Calxon Group; Backdoor listing; Value creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2009年经济超预期回暖、IPO阶段性停潮和资本市场历史性低估值带来的廉价壳资源，大批拟上市企业通过借壳实现上市，嘉凯城则是这场借壳上市狂潮中的一个经典案例。饱受“鸿仪系”“隧道行为”侵害的亚华控股，需要注入新的资产，才能走出财务危机的泥潭。在中信资本的操盘下，*ST亚华剥离了经营资产，成为一个只有8,000万元货币资金，没有其他资产、负债和人员的“壳”。浙商集团房地产业务资产通过反向购买成功“借壳”*ST亚华，公司更名为嘉凯城，一家资不抵债的*ST公司变身成为一家市值居前的房地产上市公司。这场资产重组，不仅是反向购买会计核算新规下成功借壳上市的典范，也是一个经典的产业并购案例。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The economic recovery than expected in 2009、episodic stagnation of IPO and historic low valuations of capital market bring about cheap shell resource. Lots of enterprises to be listed achieved through the backdoor listing, and China Calxon Group is a classic case of this backdoor listing mania. Suffered from “Hongyi Class” and “Tunneling”, Ava Holdings needs to inject new assets in order to go out of the mire of the financial crisis. In the operations of Citic Capital, *ST Ava stripped business assets and became a “shell” which only has 80 million yuan currency, without other assets, liabilities and personnel. Zhe Shang Group real estate business assets successfully “backdoor” *ST Ava through reverse acquisitions, and the company changed its name to China Calxon Group. An insolvent *ST company turns to a real estate listed company which has top market capitalization. This asset restructuring not only is a successful model of backdoor listing under accounting new rules about reverse acquisitions, but also a classic case of industry mergers and acquisitions.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IPO、借壳上市</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
